  "body": " References and Suggested Readings   Artin, E. Theory: Lectures Delivered at the University of Notre Dame (Notre Dame Mathematical Lectures, Number 2) . Dover, Mineola, NY, 1997.   Edwards, H. M. Galois Theory . Springer-Verlag, New York, 1984.   Fraleigh, J. B. A First Course in Abstract Algebra . 7th ed. Pearson, Upper Saddle River, NJ, 2003.   Gaal, L. Classical Galois Theory with Examples . American Mathematical Society, Providence, 1979.   Garling, D. J. H. A Course in Galois Theory . Cambridge University Press, Cambridge, 1986.   Kaplansky, I. Fields and Rings . 2nd ed. University of Chicago Press, Chicago, 1972.   Rothman, T. The Short Life of Évariste Galois,  Scientific American , April 1982, 136 49.  "
